description:
This is a 360 minute workout called 'Amelia Chill Girl Playlist ' from the channel Hugo Alexander Leon Peraza.
The workout falls under Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Groove Session and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe. The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no one’s watching and feel amazing..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
